  "detailed_description": "<h1>Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>This is an action-adventure game built for virtual reality.<br>You play as an adventurer, freely roam and explore in a medieval open world.<br>Complete a series of quests to unlock skills and upgrade equipment, and finally defeat the dragon in the hill cave.<br><br>Game features:<br>1. Day and night system, experience the scenery of the medieval world at different times.<br>2. Realistic climbing and swimming system, roaming around castles, lakes and mountains.<br>3. Realistic combat system and sound effects.<br>4. Various weapon systems can be switched freely.<br>5. Character level and skill system.<br>6. AI interactive system.<br>7. Hidden characters and treasure chests are available for exploration.<br>8. Background music is suitable for the environment.<br>9. With high graphics quality, enhance the sense of immersion.<br>10. Support DLSS (only compatible with NVIDIA RTX Graphics card)<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223010/extras/e358708fdec78be01c22478e00cb55e4.avif?t=1671958807\" width=600 height=124 /></span>",
